2008-09-21 Borut Razem <borut.razem@siol.net>
	* plat/win32/gpsim.nsi, doc/gpsimWin32.html:
	  updated for libpng-1.2.29, win_iconv_dll-tml-20080320, atk_1.22.0-2_win32,
