2006-04-13 Borut Razem <borut.razem@siol.net>
	* gui/gui_src_asm.cc: removed warnings
	* modules/switch.h, src/dspic/dspic-processors.h, src/operator.h:
	  enable compilation on Fedora Core 5 (gcc 4.1.0)
