2005-07-22 Scott Dattalo <scott@dattalo.com>
	* cli/cmd_disasm.cc: rnages were disassembling wrong addresses
	* gui/gui_src_asm.cc: cleanup
	* src/12bit-processors.cc, src/14bit-processors.cc,
